node.text:
Well. Not the news I wanted to put out but for my well being it’s the best case. 

I as well as the team have decided to take time off due to the EBV virus I have been battling all summer. I showed up and pushed through it each race but there comes a point you will keep digging yourself a deeper hole. 

Even though I was cranking out top 10s I was still no where I should be. But anyways going to take this time to rest & get my energy/blood levels back where they need to be. Thank you all for the support!

- Deano

@rockstarenergy @husqvarnamotorcyclesusa @onealracing @artificialgrassliquidators  @alpinestars @lululemon @gopro @ethika @iamspecialized @ride100percent @ctikneebraces @polarusa @dillongeorgian @sarahvanicek

node.text:
Solid day in the office. On paper not great with an 8th OA. First moto came through the pack to 8th, Moto 2 fell in the first turn came from last to 9th. My best riding of the season that moto. Just felt good to ride with a good flow. It was a hot one today to🥵 Thank you guys for the unreal support today! Let’s just keep trying to improve💪🏽
.
.
